47 he asked him from where he was, and he responded:
48 “I was born in the kingdom of Navarre.”

52 Then I was in the family of the good King Theobald;
53 there I set myself to do brokering,
54 for which I render account in this heat.”

58 Among bad cats the mouse had come;
59 but Barbariccia closed him in with her arms
60 and said: “Stay there, while I fork him.”

